    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes the CONNECT-IP HTTP method.  CONNECT-IP is
   similar to CONNECT-UDP, but allows transmitting IP packets, without
   being limited to just TCP like CONNECT or UDP like CONNECT-UDP.</t>
    </abstract>
